# Intrigue to Deprivation

.W01 — 0.0s-0.5s — Intrigue to Deprivation
CU 35mm lens, angled slightly downward for 9:16 vertical filling.
A pale, manicured hand (wearing a slightly oversized, textured cream linen sleeve) entering from the bottom right frame.
A generic, dull-yellow plastic pharmacy lip balm tube is aggressively flicked into a matte-grey metal wire mesh trash bin. The motion is fast, ending with the tube hitting the bottom of the bin.
Harsh, overhead fluorescent with a deliberate sickening green/cyan cast. Deep, unforgiving shadows under the rim of the bin.
Kinetic handheld snap zoom pushing into the bin precisely as the plastic tube hits the metal. Shallow depth of field blurs the background to focus entirely on the discarded object. Sets the 'deprivation' tone instantly.

[[AUDIO: Ambient: Stark, sterile fluorescent overhead hum, creating an immediate sense of cold discomfort. | SFX: Sharp, aggressive plastic-on-metal clatter as the cheap lip balm hits the bottom of the wire bin. | Music: Abrupt, dissonant low-frequency drone that starts on frame one and sharply cuts off, leaving an uneasy tension under the single word VO.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
Swapped

.W02 — 0.5s-5.0s — Intrigue to Deprivation
MS 24mm wide, positioned at chest-height, capturing from the waist up to the top of the head in vertical crop.
A late-20s woman with a messy low bun, wearing the cream linen button-down. Posture is slumped, micro-expression is a deadpan, exhausted stare directly into the lens. Lips appear visibly dry.
She looks up from the trash bin, locks eyes with the camera, sighs, and reaches into a structured leather tote bag slung over her shoulder. She pulls out the premium lip balm—a heavy, square-based clear jar with a stark white and brushed silver lid.
Sterile breakroom lighting continues: overhead fluorescent with a green cast, creating flat, uncomplimentary mid-tones that emphasize fatigue.
Static camera. The set dressing in the deep background features a drab water cooler and pale beige walls. The contrast of the sleek, architectural silver/white jar against the mundane background signals the intrusion of luxury.

_TEXT SUPER: Ditch the basics._

[[AUDIO: Ambient: Muffled, distant office air conditioning drone and lifeless breakroom room-tone. | SFX: Heavy rustle of a structured leather tote bag, followed by the solid, premium clack of the heavy glass jar being pulled out. | Music: A sustained, hollow sub-bass note that implies confinement and exhaustion. Volume dips heavily to carve space for the 14-word VO delivery.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
the mundane for a wild strawberry and pomegranate escape. I am never looking back.

# Ritual to Exaltation

.W03 — 5.0s-7.0s — Ritual to Exaltation
ECU 85mm macro lens, locked directly onto the lower half of the face.
The creator's lips and chin. Skin texture shows slight dehydration. No makeup is visible.
She presses her lips together in a tight, uncomfortable line, rubbing the upper and lower lip against each other to emphasize friction and dryness.
Top-down, high-contrast lighting highlighting the dry texture of the lips. No fill light, emphasizing shadows in the corners of the mouth.
Locked off camera. Focus peaks sharply on the center of the bottom lip. This shot must physically communicate a dry, uncomfortable sensory feeling.

_TEXT SUPER: AC dryness hitting hard?_

[[AUDIO: Ambient: Ultra-close, dry acoustic room tone, completely stripped of any reverberation to isolate the physical friction. | SFX: Visceral, dry, abrasive skin-rubbing texture, hyper-focused to communicate the physical discomfort of dehydrated lips. | Music: The hollow sub-bass note fades into a tense, expectant atmospheric void. Sparse, minimal instrumentation.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
Because the ordinary everyday lacks magic.

.W04 — 7.0s-12.0s — Ritual to Exaltation
CU 50mm lens, top-down angle focusing on the hands holding the jar.
Both hands, framed tightly within the vertical borders. The left hand firmly grips the clear square base; the right hand rests on the levitating opaque white lid.
The right hand twists the brushed silver metallic rim. As the lid comes off, a visceral shock of saturated, juicy crimson balm is revealed inside the vault-like jar.
The lighting suddenly shifts mid-action. The harsh green overhead cuts out, replaced by a soft, warm golden hour directional light spilling from the left frame, hitting the glossy surface of the red balm.
Smooth, slow push-in on a dolly. As the lid is removed, the transition in lighting acts as a visual 'breath'. The set dressing transitions out of focus to a warm, bright wooden vanity surface.

_TEXT SUPER: Unlock raw botanical potency._

[[AUDIO: Ambient: The sterile room tone abruptly drops out mid-action, replaced by a warm, resonant, expanding atmospheric wash. | SFX: Heavy, metallic twist of the brushed silver lid, followed by a soft pneumatic release as the airtight seal is broken. | Music: Warm, analog synth pads enter with a gentle swell, marking the transition from deprivation to ritual. The mix carefully ducks under the deliberate VO pacing.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
This is the deliberate pause. A quiet, tactile shift into something sacred, strictly for me.

.W05 — 12.0s-14.0s — Ritual to Exaltation
Extreme Macro 100mm lens. The jar fills the entire bottom third; the finger fills the top.
The index finger of the creator, perfectly manicured, hovering just above the jar.
The pad of the index finger presses slowly and deliberately into the vibrant, fleshy crimson concentrate. The glossy surface yields slightly, coating the fingertip in a rich red glaze.
Soft warm golden backlight creating a rim light on the fingertip, with a silver bounce board front-right illuminating the deep berry-red interior of the balm.
Locked off. The shallow depth of field isolates the exact point of contact. This shot triggers raw tactile curiosity and appetite. The movement is ASMR-level slow.

[[AUDIO: Ambient: A near-absolute vacuum of background sound to completely center the viewer's attention on the tactile interaction. | SFX: Hyper-detailed, ASMR-grade slow squelch and glossy, sticky glide as the finger presses into the yielding crimson concentrate. | Music: Music drops out entirely. Absolute focus on the tactile ASMR sound to preserve an unbroken trance-like aesthetic.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
[SILENT]

.W06 — 14.0s-18.0s — Ritual to Exaltation
ECU 85mm lens. Framing the lower face and the right hand entering from the right side of the vertical frame.
The creator, now radiating calm confidence. Shoulders relaxed. The texture of her cream linen shirt is visible in the lower edge of the frame.
She physically applies the glossy crimson balm directly to her lower lip with her coated index finger. The smooth glide instantly transforms the dry texture into a hydrated, plump, vibrant red finish. She finishes with a soft, relaxed smile.
Bright, beautiful everyday on-the-go window light. Soft, diffused daylight wrapping entirely around her face from the left, with a subtle white bounce on the right for flawless, glowing skin.
This is the mandatory scene. Slow, handheld drift to imply a relaxed, organic vlog style, yet flawlessly lit. The background is a bright, sunlit modern bathroom with blurred white tile and a green pothos plant out of focus. Complete symbolic transformation.

[[AUDIO: Ambient: Soft, airy acoustic presence of a sunlit bathroom, with the faintest hint of a gentle morning breeze outside the window. | SFX: Smooth, slick, hydrating glide sound of the balm coating the lips, followed by a subtle, relaxed exhalation of breath from the creator. | Music: Warm, ethereal pads return, introducing a slow, rhythmic, heartbeat-like sub-kick at 60 BPM to signify emotional and physical calm. Intensity recedes under VO.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
Instant revival. A sudden wave of comfort bringing me right back to center.

.W07 — 18.0s-26.0s — Ritual to Exaltation
MCU 50mm lens, eye-level. Subject is framed from mid-chest to just above the head.
The creator, holding the open silver-rimmed jar up near her cheek. Her lips are vibrant and hydrated. Her expression is exalted and at peace.
She tilts her head slightly, catching the natural light on her freshly hydrated lips, and turns the jar slightly so the deep forest green and stark black typography faces the camera.
Continued bright, diffused natural window light. The lighting highlights the 'glass skin' aesthetic and the glossy finish of the lip balm.
Camera pushes in slowly. The focus is split perfectly between her glowing face and the premium apothecary styling of the jar. Negative fill on the right side adds cinematic contrast to her jawline.

_TEXT SUPER: COSMOS Approved. 100% Plant-Based._
_TEXT SUPER: Instant aesthetic revival._

[[AUDIO: Ambient: Gentle, serene atmospheric room tone that reinforces the bright, diffused natural daylight. | SFX: Subtle handling noise of the heavy glass jar and the faint rustle of the cream linen shirt. | Music: Cinematic, exalted swell of the ambient pads. A gentle, resonant chime is introduced in the upper register, carefully mixed to avoid frequency collision with the dense VO.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
You outgrow compromises. Choosing absolute purity is how you protect your peace. An everyday indulgence that refuses to settle.

# Offering

.W08 — 26.0s-32.0s — Offering
CU 50mm lens. Vertical tabletop setup. Frame is strictly locked off.
Exactly three heavy, square-based clear jars stacked vertically in the center of the frame. The top jar has its white and silver lid removed.
A finger enters from the top frame, performing a slow, deliberate smudge test across the juicy crimson surface of the top jar, dragging the rich texture toward the camera. The hand then exits the frame swiftly, mimicking a flicking motion that loops seamlessly back to the throwing action in W01.
Spotlight effect: Warm directional overhead light pooling directly onto the stacked jars, emphasizing the clean architectural lines and the ruby-red interior, while the background falls into a moody, deep shadow.
Crucial offer window constraint met: exactly three jars are visually stacked, word count for the super is exactly 7 words. The finger smudge provides the tactile sensory interaction required. The swift exit of the hand perfectly sets up the loop back to the abrupt toss in W01.

_TEXT SUPER: Buy 3, Save ₹200. Share the sanctuary._

[[AUDIO: Ambient: Intimate, warm studio-quiet tone. | SFX: Creamy, viscous swipe of the finger performing the smudge test, ending with a sharp, kinetic air-whoosh as the hand swiftly exits the frame to loop. | Music: Pads slowly fade out while the heartbeat kick drops away. The lingering warm ambient tail sharply cuts out exactly on the hand's kinetic exit, bridging perfectly into the dissonant start of W01.]]

[[LOOP NOTE: The W08 audio design currently ends with a 'sharp cut' on the ambient tail. A harsh cut breaks the seamless loop requirement. Modify the final 1-2 seconds of W08 to feature a crossfade-compatible ending by fading the warm ambient tail into a subtle, low-frequency dissonant texture that organically bridges into the abrupt drone at the start of W01.]]

CREATOR (V.O.)
An invitation to share this sanctuary with your inner circle.

